The reports generator uses nightly backups files as a source for the reports and generates the reports as soon as backups are completed.

The following file formats are supported by the framework:
* pdf files,
* excel spreadsheets,
* power point presentations.

The framework is implemented using Python scripts and runs on the server.

The Reports Generator might be installed and reports generated also on the local machine.

The generated reports are being described in the [[Help:Reports|Reports section]] of the [[Help:Wiki Model|Wiki Model]] and as a result links to generated reports are made available on the data and various meta-model pages.
